        "code": "<style>\n\n.se-settle{background:var(--bg);padding:64px 20px;box-sizing:border-box;color:var(--text);overflow:hidden;}\n.se-settle *{box-sizing:border-box;}\n.se-settle__inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}\n.se-settle__eyebrow{display:block;text-align:center;color:var(--BTN-PRIMARY-BG);font-size:var(--font-subheading);font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-SUBHEADING);font-style:var(--FONT-STYLE-SUBHEADING);font-weight:var(--FONT-WEIGHT-SUBHEADING);letter-spacing:var(--LETTER-SPACING-SUBHEADING);text-transform:var(--FONT-UPPERCASE-SUBHEADING);margin:0 0 12px;}\n.se-settle__title{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-HEADING);text-align:center;font-size:var(--font-heading-large);font-weight:800;line-height:1.45;margin:0 0 18px;color:var(--text);}\n.se-settle__lead{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);text-align:center;font-size:var(--font-body-medium);line-height:1.95;max-width:780px;margin:0 auto 44px;opacity:.92;}\n.se-settle__note{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);max-width:880px;margin:36px auto 0;padding:18px 22px;border-left:3px solid var(--BTN-PRIMARY-BG);background:rgba(0,0,0,.035);border-radius:6px;font-size:var(--font-body-small);line-height:1.85;opacity:.92;}\n@media (max-width:768px){.se-settle{padding:48px 18px;}.se-settle__lead{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);font-size:var(--font-body-medium);margin-bottom:32px;text-align:left;}.se-settle__title{line-height:1.4;}}\n\n.se-settle__box{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;font-size:var(--font-body-medium);line-height:2;opacity:.95;}\n.se-settle__box p{margin:0 0 18px;}\n.se-settle__flag{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:14px;max-width:760px;margin:6px auto 34px;}\n.se-settle__pill{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.15);}\n.se-settle__pill.is-on{background:var(--BTN-PRIMARY-BG);color:var(--BTN-PRIMARY-TEXT,#fff);border-color:var(--BTN-PRIMARY-BG);}\n.se-settle__arrow{display:flex;align-items:center;color:var(--BTN-PRIMARY-BG);font-weight:800;}\n@media (max-width:768px){.se-settle__box{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);font-size:var(--font-body-medium);line-height:1.95;}}\n</style>\n<section class=\"se-settle\">\n  <div class=\"se-settle__inner\">\n    <span class=\"se-settle__eyebrow\">Settlement</span>\n    <h2 class=\"se-settle__title\">売上は月末に集計し、<br class=\"se-sp-br2\">翌月に商品仕入代金としてお支払いします。</h2>\n    <div class=\"se-settle__image\"><div class=\"se-settle__image-inner\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0704/2642/7614/files/Wallet.jpg?v=1782459254\" alt=\"売上は月末に集計し、翌月に商品仕入代金としてお支払いします。\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\"></div></div>\n    <div class=\"se-settle__flag\">\n      <span class=\"se-settle__pill\">月末締めで販売実績を集計</span>\n      <span class=\"se-settle__arrow\">→</span>\n      <span class=\"se-settle__pill is-on\">翌月に商品仕入代金をお支払い</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"se-settle__box\">\n      <p>本プランでは、購入者からの売上はSOLSTARが受領します。販売実績に基づいて、SOLSTARがメーカー様から商品を仕入れる形になります。</p>\n      <p>そのため、メーカー様には販売実績に基づく「商品仕入代金」としてお支払いします。月末に集計し、翌月にお支払いします。</p>\n      <p>返品・返金・キャンセルが発生した場合は、契約条件に基づき精算で調整します。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<style>.se-settle__image{padding:0 0 40px;box-sizing:border-box;}.se-settle__image-inner{max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;}.se-settle__image-inner img{display:block;width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;}@media (max-width:768px){.se-settle__image{padding-bottom:32px;}.se-settle__image-inner{max-width:100%;}}.se-sp-br2{display:none;}@media(max-width:768px){.se-sp-br2{display:inline;}}</style>",
