        "code": "<style>\n\n.se-brand-data{background:var(--bg);padding:64px 20px;box-sizing:border-box;color:var(--text);overflow:hidden;}\n.se-brand-data *{box-sizing:border-box;}\n.se-brand-data__inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}\n.se-brand-data__eyebrow{display:block;text-align:center;color:var(--BTN-PRIMARY-BG);font-size:var(--font-subheading);font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-SUBHEADING);font-style:var(--FONT-STYLE-SUBHEADING);font-weight:var(--FONT-WEIGHT-SUBHEADING);letter-spacing:var(--LETTER-SPACING-SUBHEADING);text-transform:var(--FONT-UPPERCASE-SUBHEADING);margin:0 0 12px;}\n.se-brand-data__title{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-HEADING);text-align:center;font-size:var(--font-heading-large);font-weight:800;line-height:1.45;margin:0 0 18px;color:var(--text);}\n.se-brand-data__lead{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);text-align:center;font-size:var(--font-body-medium);line-height:1.95;max-width:780px;margin:0 auto 44px;opacity:.92;}\n.se-brand-data__showcase{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) minmax(320px,420px);gap:40px;align-items:center;max-width:980px;margin:0 auto;}\n.se-brand-data__content{min-width:0;}\n.se-brand-data__list{list-style:none;margin:0;padding:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:14px 24px;}\n.se-brand-data__item{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;font-size:var(--font-body-medium);line-height:1.75;padding:0;}\n.se-brand-data__chk{color:var(--BTN-PRIMARY-BG);font-weight:800;flex:0 0 auto;line-height:1.5;}\n.se-brand-data__media{position:relative;width:100%;aspect-ratio:1/1;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:rgba(0,0,0,.04);}\n.se-brand-data__media img{width:100%;height:100%;display:block;object-fit:cover;}\n.se-brand-data__divider{max-width:1100px;margin:116px auto 0;}\n.se-brand-data__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;}\n.se-brand-data__cell{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:var(--bg-accent);border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);border-radius:10px;padding:16px 18px;font-size:var(--font-body-medium);font-weight:700;}\n.se-brand-data__dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--BTN-PRIMARY-BG);flex:0 0 auto;}\n@media (max-width:900px){.se-brand-data__showcase{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:28px;}.se-brand-data__grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}.se-brand-data__media{max-width:420px;margin:0 auto;}}\n@media (max-width:768px){.se-brand-data{padding:48px 18px;}.se-brand-data__lead{font-family:var(--FONT-STACK-BODY);font-size:var(--font-body-medium);margin-bottom:32px;text-align:left;}.se-brand-data__title{line-height:1.4;}.se-brand-data__list{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:12px;}.se-brand-data__divider{margin-top:64px;}}\n@media (max-width:520px){.se-brand-data__grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}\n</style>\n<section class=\"se-brand-data\">\n  <div class=\"se-brand-data__inner\">\n    <span class=\"se-brand-data__eyebrow\">Brand</span>\n    <h2 class=\"se-brand-data__title\">ブランドイメージを守る運用ルールを事前に決めます。</h2>\n    <p class=\"se-brand-data__lead\">メーカー様の商品価値を正しく伝えるため、商品ページや販売価格、キャンペーン内容は、事前にルールを定めたうえで運用します。</p>\n    <div class=\"se-brand-data__showcase\">\n      <div class=\"se-brand-data__content\">\n        <ul class=\"se-brand-data__list\"><li class=\"se-brand-data__item\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__chk\">✓</span>ブランドコンセプトの理解</li><li class=\"se-brand-data__item\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__chk\">✓</span>販売価格の決定ルール</li><li class=\"se-brand-data__item\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__chk\">✓</span>ブランドガイドラインの共有</li><li class=\"se-brand-data__item\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__chk\">✓</span>NG表現の確認</li></ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"se-brand-data__media\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0704/2642/7614/files/Brand_Image_copy.jpg?v=1782533574\" alt=\"ブランドイメージに配慮した販売運用イメージ\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"se-brand-data__divider\">\n      <span class=\"se-brand-data__eyebrow\">Data</span>\n      <h2 class=\"se-brand-data__title\">売上改善に必要なデータを月次で共有します。</h2>\n      <p class=\"se-brand-data__lead\">本プランでは、購入者から見た販売者はSOLSTARとなります。個人を特定できる顧客情報は、配送業務に必要な範囲でのみメーカー様へ共有します。</p>\n      <div class=\"se-brand-data__grid\"><div class=\"se-brand-data__cell\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__dot\"></span>月次売上</div><div class=\"se-brand-data__cell\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__dot\"></span>注文件数</div><div class=\"se-brand-data__cell\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__dot\"></span>平均注文単価</div><div class=\"se-brand-data__cell\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__dot\"></span>売れ筋商品</div><div class=\"se-brand-data__cell\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__dot\"></span>返品・キャンセル状況</div><div class=\"se-brand-data__cell\"><span class=\"se-brand-data__dot\"></span>改善提案</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
